name: rb-jekyll-github-metadata
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "jekyll-github-metadata" %}
{% set version = "2.12.1" %}

package:
  name: rb-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://rubygems.org/downloads/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  sha256: 3744843c7e55b9e3a5fbf0478ef7e28a4433c92cb2388eeff1344ce52b5602c8

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 0
  script:
    - gem install -N -l -V --norc --ignore-dependencies {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  skip: {{ win }}

requirements:
  host:
    - ruby
  run:
    - ruby
    - rb-jekyll >=3.4,<4
    - rb-octokit >=4.0,<5,!=4.4.0

test:
  commands:
    - ruby -r jekyll -r {{ name }} -e 'exit 0'

about:
  home: https://rubygems.org/gems/{{ name }}
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: The site.github namespace

  doc_url: https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/{{ name }}
  dev_url: https://github.com/parkr/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sodre
